{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"54bbb6d2e3","title":"致彭德怀等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8b4fd0676e","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":28,"articleId":"54bbb6d2e3"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dcd6b55a8b","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"54bbb6d2e3"},{"id":"21f063adbd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月28日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"54bbb6d2e3"},{"id":"3c381aeca5","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、胡敌以我避免决战，十分轻我，向打拉池锐进，王、毛向靖远进。乙、我三个方面军主力应依兄等二十七日部署，立即集结在看利阵地，在数日内坚决突击消灭胡敌先头一个师至两个师以小部抗阻靖远王、毛。丙、九及三十军速复河岸西向中卫、定远营扫荡前进。丁、此是消灭敌人开展局势最适当之时机，请兄等速图之。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"54bbb6d2e3"},{"id":"c698d10568","type":"paragraph","text":"[11这是毛泽东和周恩来致彭德怀、朱德、张国泰电的主要内容。[21王、毛，指王均、毛炳文。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"54bbb6d2e3"}],"page":{"id":"882410b8ee","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"54bbb6d2e3","start":263,"end":263}}}},"__N_SSG":true}